## 🎯 SESSION STATE

> **Overwrite every session. This is the primary hot-restart entry point.**
> **A cold AI should be able to continue from this section alone.**

### Active objective
_One sentence: what are we building/fixing right now?_

### Context
_What must a cold AI know to continue without reading the conversation? Be specific enough to resume._

### Last action taken
_Specific enough to resume from exactly here._

### Next immediate step
_Exact action. No ambiguity. If blocked, state what is needed to unblock._

### Do NOT touch this session
_Areas frozen, under migration, or owned by another team member. Flag and stop if asked to modify._
- —

### Branch / workspace
_Branch: — · Uncommitted: — · Open PR: —_

### Blockers
- —

### Open questions
_If answerable from the codebase, answer now and delete the entry._
- —

