| Symptom | Root cause | Correct approach |
|---------|-----------|-----------------|
| — | — | — |

---

## 🗒 AI NOTES

> **Most valuable section. Append only. Newest first. Dated.**
> **Write anything that would take minutes to re-derive but seconds to recall.**
> **Severity tags: `[!]` breaks if ignored · `[~]` non-obvious gotcha · `[?]` unresolved question**

_Example:_
_`2024-03-15 [!] — The userId in the sessions table is the users.uid column, NOT users.id. Three hours lost to this.`_
_`2024-03-20 [~] — Payment webhook fires twice in sandbox, once in production. Deduplication in paymentWebhook.controller.js handles it but only with the idempotency key.`_
_`2024-03-22 [?] — Does the rate limiter reset on midnight UTC or per rolling 24h window? Not documented.`_

